author: henning
msg: This is the first part of a patch to the Turbine ACL system. It
replaces the AccessControlList Object with an interface to make it
possible to replace the standard ACL object with custom designed ACL
objects that use a different backend. The normal ACL object is renamed
to TurbineAccessControlList.
This code was written by a co-worker of mine, Marco Knuettel. He can be
reached at marco@intermeta.de
